                     <interp inst="t17880227-85-off421" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17880227-85-off421" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing six pair of womens leather shoes, value 2 s. and six pair of men's leather shoes, value 2 s.
